ctral resolution, are thus\nconfirmed by our analysis of the deep echelle spectra using the new atomic\ndata.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2016 12:08:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-27"}
